root: ^Hello my child, would you be so dear as to help a lady in need?
^Some monsters stole all my clothes and ran away into my mansion, would you be so kind as to get them back to me?
^They have taken my dress, my hat, and my underwear.
^Here, take this key to get in. I always keep a spare on my necklace.
^I would go in myself, but it's a bit embarrassing.
^Please hurry, it is getting late and the air grows cold...
